I need the API access token

To get an API access token, you need to request it through the nova-adops-performance-escalation Slack channel. Please provide your Organization ID and the email attached to your organization in the request.
How do I get access to that slack channel

To get access to the nova-adops-performance-escalation Slack channel, you will need to contact your organization's admin or IT department. They should be able to provide you with the necessary access or invite you to the channel.
